''Optional:'' Complete the steps below if unfamiliar with GnuPG or if they haven't already been performed. This will fix eventual {{Code2|gpg: WARNING: unsafe ownership}} warnings.

Have GnuPG initialize your user data folder.

{{CodeSelect|code=
gpg --fingerprint
}}

Set warning free permissions.

{{CodeSelect|code=
chmod --recursive og-rwx ~/.gnupg
}}